## Environment Variables

Set in **Vercel Dashboard → Project → Settings → Environment Variables** (not in `.env`, which is not deployed).

### Required for OAuth to work

| Variable | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `REDIS_URL` | Redis connection URL (`rediss://...`) — from Upstash or Vercel KV |
| `SESSION_SECRET` | 32+ char random string. `node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"` |
| `PINGONE_ENVIRONMENT_ID` | PingOne env ID |
| `PINGONE_REGION` | `com` / `eu` / `ca` / `asia` |
| `PINGONE_AI_CORE_CLIENT_ID` | Admin OAuth app client ID |
| `PINGONE_AI_CORE_CLIENT_SECRET` | Admin OAuth app client secret |
| `PINGONE_AI_CORE_REDIRECT_URI` | `https://<url>/api/auth/oauth/callback` |
| `PINGONE_AI_CORE_USER_CLIENT_ID` | User OAuth app client ID |
| `PINGONE_AI_CORE_USER_REDIRECT_URI` | `https://<url>/api/auth/oauth/user/callback` |
| `REACT_APP_CLIENT_URL` | Frontend URL (for post-logout redirect) |

### Required for MCP / Banking Agent

| Variable | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `MCP_SERVER_URL` | `wss://your-mcp-server-host` |

### Optional but useful

| Variable | Default | Description |
|----------|---------|-------------|
| `CORS_ORIGIN` | production URL | Explicit CORS origin |
| `CIBA_ENABLED` | `false` | Enable CIBA flows |
| `STEP_UP_AMOUNT_THRESHOLD` | `250` | Dollar amount triggering MFA step-up |
| `STEP_UP_ACR_VALUE` | `Multi_factor` | DaVinci policy ACR value for step-up |
| `DEMO_MODE` | `true` | Disable destructive operations on shared deployments |
| `DEBUG_OAUTH` | `false` | Verbose OAuth logging (never true in prod) |
| `SKIP_TOKEN_SIGNATURE_VALIDATION` | — | **FATAL if `true` in production** — server exits at startup |
| `PUBLIC_APP_URL` | auto-detected | Override redirect URI base URL (custom domain) |

### Upstash / Redis Setup (Free Tier)

1. Go to [upstash.com](https://upstash.com) → Create database → Copy `REDIS_URL`
2. Or: Vercel Dashboard → Storage → Add Upstash KV integration → auto-injects `UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL` + `UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN`
3. The server auto-detects both — `REDIS_URL` takes priority over Upstash env vars

