## Deploying

```bash
# Deploy to production (from repo root)
npm run build --prefix banking_api_ui   # build React first
vercel --prod

# Or the full pipeline:
npm run build --prefix banking_api_ui && git add -A && git commit -m "..." && git push origin main && vercel --prod
```

**After deploying, always:**
1. Verify redirect URIs in PingOne match the new deployment URL
2. Check `GET /api/auth/oauth/redirect-info` for the detected redirect URIs
3. First login after a new deploy may hit a cold-start delay (~3-5s)

