## Common Deployment Issues

| Symptom | Cause | Fix |
|---------|-------|-----|
| Login fails with `invalid_state` | No Redis → sessions lost across instances | Add `REDIS_URL` |
| Callback shows `nonce_mismatch` | Same as above | Add `REDIS_URL` |
| Secure cookie not set | `trust proxy` missing or `SESSION_SECRET` wrong | Verify `app.set('trust proxy', 1)` + strong `SESSION_SECRET` |
| Server exits immediately | `SKIP_TOKEN_SIGNATURE_VALIDATION=true` in prod OR weak `SESSION_SECRET` | Remove the var / set real secret |
| MCP panel shows "connecting..." forever | `MCP_SERVER_URL` not set or WebSocket server down | Set `MCP_SERVER_URL`, check MCP server host |
| Redirect URI mismatch | PingOne registered URI ≠ actual deployment URL | Update PingOne app redirect URIs to match Vercel URL |
| Build fails with TypeScript errors | `CI=false` might be missing in build env | Ensure `"CI": "false"` in `vercel.json` build.env |
